#!/bin/sh
echo "Restarting kqp..."
systemctl restart kqp.service
# end

data.name: action_log
data.script:
-- action_log.moon
lunit = require 'lunit'
lpfrag = lunit.lpfrag

{
  name:     'log'
  desc:     '증적 LOG 기록 함수'
  aliases:  {'kpass','증적로그','로그기록','증적로그기록'}

  fn:       (o,opt)->
            -- print '','action-log:',(to_json opt)

            try_rule o,opt

            o.fnid = opt.fnid  if opt.fnid
            o.app = opt.app  if opt.app
            o.instcode = opt.inst  if opt.inst

            TO_AUDITLOG o,opt.to
            o.app = nil
            o.fnid = nil

}

#!/bin/sh
echo "Starting kqp..."
systemctl start kqp.service
# end
